280
00:18:13,765 --> 00:18:15,285
What should I sing?

281
00:18:18,765 --> 00:18:20,365
Hey, Qingqing?

282
00:18:21,005 --> 00:18:21,965
Qingqing?

283
00:18:31,125 --> 00:18:32,125
Good night.

284
00:18:42,245 --> 00:18:43,165
Chen Qingqing.

285
00:18:43,245 --> 00:18:45,285
I'm not around. Who are you going
to see a movie with?

286
00:18:45,365 --> 00:18:46,285
How did you know?

287
00:18:46,365 --> 00:18:48,805
I've planted an informer around you.

288
00:18:49,285 --> 00:18:50,725
It's Gu Nanxi, right?

289
00:18:51,285 --> 00:18:52,245
Don't change the topic.

290
00:18:52,365 --> 00:18:53,765
Tell me. Who's going with you?

291
00:18:53,965 --> 00:18:56,005
Fangfang doesn't have to work today,

292
00:18:56,365 --> 00:18:57,845
so we decided to go watch a movie.

293
00:18:58,005 --> 00:18:58,925
All right.

294
00:18:59,005 --> 00:19:00,645
Go to the movies with me when I come back.

295
00:19:00,725 --> 00:19:01,725
I pity myself.

296
00:19:01,805 --> 00:19:03,405
I've only watched a few movies this year.

297
00:19:09,365 --> 00:19:10,205
Chen Qingqing.

298
00:19:12,845 --> 00:19:13,925
Welcome back.

299
00:19:14,005 --> 00:19:15,045
Come on.

300
00:19:15,205 --> 00:19:16,725
I've arranged a celebration for you.

301
00:19:17,005 --> 00:19:17,965
Let's go eat together.

302
00:19:18,045 --> 00:19:19,485
Thank you, Lin Yiyang.

303
00:19:19,765 --> 00:19:21,765
I'm going to the movies with Fangfang.

304
00:19:22,565 --> 00:19:23,445
I'm busy.

305
00:19:23,525 --> 00:19:24,845
Aren't you going to eat?

306
00:19:25,405 --> 00:19:26,285
Let's eat together.

307
00:19:27,245 --> 00:19:28,805
I'm not hungry. I don't want to eat.

308
00:19:30,645 --> 00:19:31,525
-Qingqing.
-Fangfang.

309
00:19:31,605 --> 00:19:33,565
I'm so hungry. Let's go eat.

310
00:19:36,685 --> 00:19:37,565
Perfect.

311
00:19:38,445 --> 00:19:40,685
I've reserved a table
at the restaurant across the street.

312
00:19:40,765 --> 00:19:42,045
Let's go eat together.

313
00:19:42,125 --> 00:19:43,125
It's a free meal.

314
00:19:46,085 --> 00:19:47,125
Let's go eat.

315
00:19:58,965 --> 00:20:00,125
Feel free to order anything.

316
00:20:00,205 --> 00:20:01,405
You don't have to be modest.

317
00:20:03,405 --> 00:20:04,245
Chen Qingqing.

318
00:20:05,325 --> 00:20:08,925
I think you look prettier
after you came back from your hometown.

319
00:20:14,765 --> 00:20:17,085
What's gotten into Lin Yiyang?

320
00:20:17,165 --> 00:20:18,765
He just complimented me.

321
00:20:19,085 --> 00:20:20,765
Did you hear that? Pretty?

322
00:20:29,925 --> 00:20:31,085
Well,

323
00:20:31,885 --> 00:20:33,765
I think I will go to the bathroom first.

324
00:20:36,365 --> 00:20:37,405
I know this place well.

325
00:20:37,885 --> 00:20:38,845
Let me take you there.

326
00:20:39,045 --> 00:20:40,365
I can go there on my own.

327
00:20:40,765 --> 00:20:42,125
I need to go to the bathroom too.

328
00:20:51,805 --> 00:20:52,645
Chen Qingqing.

329
00:20:53,325 --> 00:20:54,765
I want to talk to you alone.

330
00:20:54,845 --> 00:20:56,925
There's nothing
that we need to discuss alone.

331
00:20:57,005 --> 00:20:58,245
Fangfang is waiting for me.

332
00:20:58,325 --> 00:20:59,205
Qingchen.

333
00:21:01,205 --> 00:21:02,405
Or

334
00:21:03,245 --> 00:21:04,485
should I call you

335
00:21:04,845 --> 00:21:07,645
the granddaughter of Chen Xiaotian,
the wealthiest man in Jincheng?

336
00:21:08,205 --> 00:21:09,285
Chen Qingqing.

337
00:21:09,645 --> 00:21:10,565
Did you investigate me?

338
00:21:15,125 --> 00:21:16,125
Chen Qingqing.

339
00:21:16,925 --> 00:21:19,205
You blew your cover by going home.

340
00:21:19,685 --> 00:21:20,525
No.

341
00:21:21,845 --> 00:21:23,325
Actually, your background

342
00:21:24,445 --> 00:21:25,765
simply catches people's attention.

343
00:21:27,525 --> 00:21:28,405
But don't worry.

344
00:21:28,485 --> 00:21:30,005
I'm not interested in you.

345
00:21:31,125 --> 00:21:32,045
One more thing.

346
00:21:33,485 --> 00:21:34,565
Stay away from Situ Feng.

347
00:21:35,045 --> 00:21:36,805
What does this have to do with Situ Feng?

348
00:21:37,725 --> 00:21:38,725
I know.

349
00:21:39,085 --> 00:21:40,285
You two are close.

350
00:21:40,765 --> 00:21:42,205
But have you ever thought about it?

351
00:21:43,205 --> 00:21:44,845
If Situ Feng finds out

352
00:21:45,525 --> 00:21:46,925
that you've been lying to him,

353
00:21:47,525 --> 00:21:48,485
what will happen?

354
00:21:49,885 --> 00:21:52,885
If the press and Situ Feng's fans find out

355
00:21:53,765 --> 00:21:55,565
that he has been lying to them,

356
00:21:57,205 --> 00:21:58,445
what's going to happen?

357
00:21:58,685 --> 00:22:01,885
"A liar who has fooled his fans."
This kind of negative coverage

358
00:22:02,485 --> 00:22:04,245
will ruin his reputation.

359
00:22:04,325 --> 00:22:07,365
Lin Yiyang, you're distorting the truth.

360
00:22:07,445 --> 00:22:08,805
No one will believe you.

361
00:22:09,565 --> 00:22:11,765
I can make up any scandals.

362
00:22:12,365 --> 00:22:13,205
By the way,

363
00:22:13,605 --> 00:22:15,445
Situ Feng is about

364
00:22:15,685 --> 00:22:16,805
to release his new album.

365
00:22:18,165 --> 00:22:21,005
Imagine how his reputation

366
00:22:21,485 --> 00:22:23,645
could be destroyed by you.

367
00:22:24,645 --> 00:22:26,285
Why are you doing this to Situ Feng?

368
00:22:26,845 --> 00:22:28,965
Because he doesn't deserve love.

369
00:22:29,045 --> 00:22:30,285
Is this because of Lan Xinyu?

370
00:22:31,725 --> 00:22:33,965
It happened a long time ago.

371
00:22:34,045 --> 00:22:36,885
-Lin Yiyang, why can't you let it go?
-Chen Qingqing.

372
00:22:38,965 --> 00:22:39,805
You don't understand.

373
00:22:43,005 --> 00:22:45,485
Anyway, Situ Feng's career
is in your hands.

374
00:22:46,605 --> 00:22:47,685
It's up to you.

375
00:22:49,445 --> 00:22:50,765
Let's go.

376
00:22:56,525 --> 00:22:58,565
Qingqing, what took you two so long?

377
00:22:58,805 --> 00:22:59,965
They've served all the dishes.

378
00:23:02,845 --> 00:23:04,005
Go ahead and eat.

379
00:23:04,085 --> 00:23:05,365
What happened just now,

380
00:23:06,365 --> 00:23:07,845
you know I didn't do it on purpose.

381
00:23:08,205 --> 00:23:09,085
I hope

382
00:23:09,765 --> 00:23:11,085
that we could get along peacefully

383
00:23:11,805 --> 00:23:12,645
from now on.

384
00:23:16,365 --> 00:23:18,605
Welcome back, Chen Qingqing.

385
00:23:33,125 --> 00:23:35,405
Is the movie over?
Can you talk on the phone now?

386
00:24:03,925 --> 00:24:05,565
Qingqing, why don't you answer it?

387
00:24:06,205 --> 00:24:07,165
It's just a crank call.

388
00:24:12,085 --> 00:24:13,325
Hello, Gu Nanxi?

389
00:24:14,605 --> 00:24:15,725
Qingqing is right next to me.

390
00:24:15,885 --> 00:24:16,885
I'm not here.

391
00:24:18,725 --> 00:24:21,485
She has fallen asleep.
Should I wake her up?

392
00:24:25,365 --> 00:24:26,405
All right, bye.

393
00:24:31,005 --> 00:24:33,485
Situ Feng must've made Gu Nanxi call you
in order to talk to me.

394
00:24:35,885 --> 00:24:37,125
What happened between you two?

395
00:24:38,645 --> 00:24:40,605
We had a small fight.

396
00:24:41,125 --> 00:24:42,165
It's not a big deal.

397
00:24:45,565 --> 00:24:46,845
You've worked hard.

398
00:24:46,925 --> 00:24:48,005
Go home and get some rest.

399
00:24:48,205 --> 00:24:50,445
We'll soon start promoting your new album.

400
00:24:50,725 --> 00:24:52,125
Daniel, take me back to school.

401
00:24:52,205 --> 00:24:53,445
There's something I need to do.

402
00:24:53,525 --> 00:24:54,885
What do you want to do there?

403
00:24:54,965 --> 00:24:56,485
Go home and rest first.

404
00:24:57,085 --> 00:24:58,165
Go back to school first.

405
00:24:59,045 --> 00:25:00,205
All right. I'll listen to you.

406
00:25:00,365 --> 00:25:01,205
Back to school.

407
00:25:02,445 --> 00:25:03,565
Come on. Let's go.

408
00:25:11,245 --> 00:25:13,125
Talk to him.
I'll go back to the dorm first.

409
00:25:24,645 --> 00:25:25,965
When did you come back?

410
00:25:26,205 --> 00:25:27,965
I came here straight from the airport.

411
00:25:28,045 --> 00:25:29,765
You must be exhausted
from all the training.

412
00:25:29,845 --> 00:25:31,205
Why didn't you go home and rest?

413
00:25:31,765 --> 00:25:32,725
Because...

414
00:25:35,405 --> 00:25:36,605
I miss you.

415
00:25:41,365 --> 00:25:42,205
Qingqing.

416
00:25:43,725 --> 00:25:45,205
I've been standing here for too long.

417
00:25:46,245 --> 00:25:47,125
My legs are numb.

418
00:25:47,205 --> 00:25:48,725
Can you give me a hand?

419
00:25:49,365 --> 00:25:50,365
Sure.

420
00:25:50,525 --> 00:25:51,485
Give it to me.

421
00:25:52,205 --> 00:25:53,165
No.

422
00:25:54,565 --> 00:25:55,525
You're so stupid.

423
00:26:00,765 --> 00:26:01,765
Qingqing.

424
00:26:02,645 --> 00:26:03,845
Why didn't you answer my calls?

425
00:26:07,325 --> 00:26:08,765
My battery ran out.

426
00:26:09,805 --> 00:26:10,885
I see.

427
00:26:19,805 --> 00:26:20,645
Qingqing.

428
00:26:26,205 --> 00:26:27,165
Have you eaten yet?

429
00:26:29,485 --> 00:26:31,205
Is there something
that you want to ask me?

430
00:26:32,085 --> 00:26:33,205
Go ahead and ask.

431
00:26:35,525 --> 00:26:38,645
I have a feeling that you're avoiding me.

432
00:26:40,445 --> 00:26:41,285
Why is that?

433
00:26:48,805 --> 00:26:49,765
Do you remember

434
00:26:50,885 --> 00:26:52,085
when you were at my place,

435
00:26:53,485 --> 00:26:55,205
I promised to give you an answer?

436
00:26:56,245 --> 00:26:57,285
I remember.

437
00:27:02,685 --> 00:27:03,525
When I came back,

438
00:27:05,685 --> 00:27:07,285
I thought hard about it.

439
00:27:11,485 --> 00:27:12,485
So...

440
00:27:14,045 --> 00:27:15,525
I have the answer now.

441
00:27:19,365 --> 00:27:20,365
Do you want to hear it?

442
00:27:21,845 --> 00:27:22,725
Yes.

443
00:27:26,885 --> 00:27:28,085
I think...

444
00:27:33,365 --> 00:27:34,205
I think

445
00:27:35,285 --> 00:27:37,765
it's better for us to stay as classmates.

446
00:27:39,165 --> 00:27:40,605
As normal friends.

447
00:27:56,245 --> 00:27:57,325
Are you sure about this?

448
00:28:01,205 --> 00:28:02,645
Don't you like me at all?

449
00:28:05,085 --> 00:28:05,965
Yes.

450
00:28:07,525 --> 00:28:08,445
I'm sure about it.

451
00:28:11,885 --> 00:28:12,845
I don't like you at all.

452
00:28:15,085 --> 00:28:17,085
Oh, right. I still have work to do.

453
00:28:17,605 --> 00:28:18,445
I have to go back.

454
00:28:50,005 --> 00:28:52,005
Qingqing, Situ Feng is in trouble.

455
00:28:52,085 --> 00:28:53,165
What happened?

456
00:28:56,765 --> 00:28:58,885
IDOL SINGER, SITU FENG,
IS ACCUSED OF PLAGIARIZING.

457
00:28:59,685 --> 00:29:00,885
How did this happen?

458
00:29:00,965 --> 00:29:03,165
Situ Feng released his new album today.

459
00:29:03,245 --> 00:29:04,405
Many people soon discovered

460
00:29:04,485 --> 00:29:07,285
that this song is very similar
to another original song on the internet.

461
00:29:07,365 --> 00:29:08,925
Although I don't know much about music,

462
00:29:09,005 --> 00:29:12,045
a lot of musicians have pointed out
that there's a possibility of plagiarism.

463
00:29:12,125 --> 00:29:14,965
After all, that song
was released two weeks ago.

464
00:29:15,045 --> 00:29:17,925
Therefore,
the press is talking about this matter.

465
00:29:20,645 --> 00:29:24,765
Wounds are smoothened by memories

466
00:29:24,845 --> 00:29:27,405
Thank you for being here

467
00:29:28,165 --> 00:29:31,485
There are too many memories

468
00:29:32,365 --> 00:29:36,005
Our worlds begin to cross path

469
00:29:36,485 --> 00:29:38,165
Where is Situ Feng right now?

470
00:29:38,245 --> 00:29:39,445
Does he know about this?

471
00:29:39,525 --> 00:29:40,445
I've just asked him.

472
00:29:40,525 --> 00:29:42,805
He's at the agency.
He probably has heard of it.

473
00:29:43,365 --> 00:29:46,205
Gu Nanxi, there's something I need to do.
I have to go back to my dorm.

474
00:29:57,085 --> 00:29:59,445
There's no way to prevent a thief
who lives under your roof.

475
00:29:59,525 --> 00:30:00,765
Did I give you my permission?

476
00:30:03,045 --> 00:30:04,205
Lin Yiyang.

477
00:30:04,285 --> 00:30:06,805
I knew you were the one who did it.

478
00:30:06,885 --> 00:30:09,525
There's no evidence to prove
that we stole the music sheet.

479
00:30:09,605 --> 00:30:11,885
I'm going to do everything
to make him miserable.

480
00:30:11,965 --> 00:30:13,485
Stop me if you can.

481
00:30:13,925 --> 00:30:14,925
Quit now.

482
00:30:15,005 --> 00:30:18,285
Quit? What's in your head?

483
00:30:18,365 --> 00:30:20,765
I didn't know Situ Feng
was this kind of person.

484
00:30:20,845 --> 00:30:23,645
I've recorded what you said.

485
00:30:23,725 --> 00:30:27,925
Situ Feng's reputation will be ruined.

486
00:30:29,805 --> 00:30:31,645
Subtitle translation by Judy Lu
